{"tid":1547760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聽日支線•自保】香港經濟面臨動盪，趁聽日換美金最後窗口！","createTime":"2019-09-06T18:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:43:20.000Z","uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ddbd1f50251c1b1a445ac67f267e176957e2d7","tid":1547760,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:53:59.000Z","msg":"【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439205</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n相信大家有睇新聞都知，香港經濟出咗唔少事。<br />\n1.大陸嘅恒大集團還唔起債<br />\n2.金管局系統故障，無法處理衍生產品交易<br />\n3.金價大跌<br />\n4.惠普降低對香港嘅評級標準<br />\n5.人行將會降準放水<br />\n<br />\n大陸冧檔震盪香港股市事小，金管局借俾大陸筆美金還唔清事大。趁依加銀行仲有得撳，大家請把握機會去撳。<br />\n擇日不如撞日，各位遊客如果早咗小小到青衣，又冇嘢做嘅，不妨去撳一下，不求錢多，但求人多。"},{"pid":"4a3ce6ea8f21bed0d8dfaf2b414bcca07758753e","tid":1547760,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:54:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"241c92e86a7a7358e7895c4dbf81c4c8b207e5dc","tid":1547760,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4558888304228167c461970039021e7b39ee480","tid":1547760,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cWpmiVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWpmiVy.jpg&h=5540436c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zqni5ts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzqni5ts.jpg&h=45208923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.